{
  "stem": "4345.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know like a line in the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know that is-- that-- And in front of them, you-- we saw as we came closer and closer, objects like killing objects.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, you could see rocks, you could see-- you could bottles, you could see clubs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said to myself, I said what-- what-- what is this?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Wasn't--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as soon as we approach them, within enough distance, all these deadly objects started to fly at us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I look at those young kids-- they were no more than 13, 14 years old, 15, with the yellow shorts, with the-- with the yellow suits with their red little things and the [? boat-- ?] It was the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is what they were trying to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the blood started to cover the faces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to duck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know where to hide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our bodies were so fragile, so thin, so sick, and the clothes was not heavy, so the bottles penetrated the-- the glass.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were cut, we were--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know something?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With all this, I survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we went through this thing so fast, and I thought to myself, this is the civilized Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My uncles lived in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother brought us there, my father had his brother there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had family, cousins.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said this is this culture that they-- they-- The civilized country with the knowledge and-- and-- and with everything and this is what they use the knowledge for, for mass murder of human beings?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So here you are.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We are teaching education to children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I try to educate them that with knowledge, with love and with knowledge, we can overcome.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we must be able to use the knowledge for the good of humanity.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
